high_descs: Turn around and then left to find the stove.
Pick up the pan from the left back burner.
Carry the pan and turn around. Turn left to find the sink.
Put the pan in the sink and turn on the water. Turn off the water and pick up the pan.
Carry the pan and take a few steps to the right.
Place the pan on the counter, to the left side.
anns.task_desc: Clean a pan and place it on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around and go left to face the stove.
Pick the pan up from the stove.
Turn around and go to the left to face the sink.
Put the pan in the sink and turn the water on and then off and then pick the pan up again.
Go right to face the counter to the right of the sink.
Put the pan down on the counter.
anns.task_desc: Put a clean pan down on the counter.

high_descs: Turn around, make a left and walk across the kitchen to the stove.
Pick up the pan on the stove.
Turn around and make a left to walk towards the sink.
Wash the pan in the sink.
Walk to the countertop where the strainer and knife are laying.
Put the pan on the countertop next to the strainer and knife.
anns.task_desc: Wash the pan sitting on the stove, letting it dry on the counter afterwards.
